name: com.rotaryheart.serializabledictionarylite
description:
Serialized Dictionary is an easy to use system that allows you to have a Dictionary being serializable and editable on the inspector.

There is no limit to what to use as a Key or as a Value, other than it being a Unity serializable type.

It comes with an easy to use and friendly UI that has the following features:

-Re ordering (Drag & Drop)
-Pages System
-Custom drawer for key or value
